						 <p>Well, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bellbloom" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2828072&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1563208466" alt="Bellbloom" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2828072)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bellbloom" >Bellbloom</a></span> a couple posts up, your wish has been granted. We’ve hit +200!! This is my third article ever to reach such a milestone, and the second article tagged with WWS to do so (makes sense, it spawned the GoI). Thanks y’all for reading this weird thing. Makes me a happy camper :D</p> 
				 	]]>
