				<wikidot:authorName>Monteparnas</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2926286</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Nice skip. I would just change the references to the Boring Agreement to a footnote, they seem too out of place in the Containment, really stands out as something that shouldn't be there. Aside from that, I would recommend on scratching out the BK name and making it a fictional or unidentified fast food chain.</p> <p>Otherwise it was excellent. The subtle anomaly that almost pass undetected until something nudges it to cause a highly unusual incident. The way WWS plays their part showing how they are far less strict than the Foundation, but still professional and cautious, the mystery left unsolved of the third party that most likely gave the BK to the crows. You did a great work here.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
