					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5215724#post-3741013</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5215724/scp-3466#post-3741013</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 16 Mar 2018 23:56:01 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>keiya</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>404549</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I love it. Profoundly <em>weird</em>, but not malicious. The Foundation acting pragmatically by making an agreement with people who were already dealing with an area's oddities rather than trying to take over and losing the institutional knowledge. The fact that the solution was fundamentally to <em>promote the crows to upper management</em> to keep them happy while providing the human customers an experience no odder than any other Burger King.</p> <p>Also the crows are better at getting orders right than the teenagers at my local Burger King.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
