						 <p>Thank you guys! We hit +100! Uber thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2320004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1519761004" alt="Rimple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2320004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" >Rimple</a></span> for supplying me the idea for my second article to ever get over +100, and this got there much faster than the other one (<a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2728">SCP-2728</a>). Thank you thank you thank you all!</p> <p><br /></p> <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><span style="font-size:400%;"><strong>HUZZAH!</strong></span></p> <p><span style="font-size:80%;">Hopefully next time I can get to this milestone with a <em>completely</em> original idea, but ah well, this was awesome anyways!</span></p> </div> 
				 	]]>
