					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5215724#post-3706788</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5215724/scp-3466#post-3706788</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2018 03:04:27 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>DarkStuff</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1581620</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I know the crows are the focus of this article, but the GoI, Wilson’s Wildlife Solutions, is my pride of it. Setting up a unique relationship to the Foundation in a concise manner and with them as a secondary focus — and further making a GoI that handles anomalies in a way that others don’t — was my favourite part of the article. I’m glad to have someone comment on it, makes my time spent thinking on it feel worth it.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5215724#post-3706778</guid>
