				<wikidot:authorName>PeppersGhost</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1553042</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is great. Using a GoI as a Foundation ally is pretty remarkable (has that happened before??) but it feels reasonable in this context.</p> <p>Also, as much as I like animal skips, it’s a refreshing change of pace to have crows that are anomalously intelligent, but not quite human-level intelligent.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
