					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5215724#post-3706446</guid>
				<title>Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5215724/scp-3466#post-3706446</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2018 17:21:49 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>DarkStuff</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1581620</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">caw?</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">caCAW</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"><img src="http://www.scp-wiki.net/local--files/scp-3466/burgerbird" alt="burgerbird" class="image" /><br /> <img src="http://www.scp-wiki.net/local--files/scp-3466/crowbusiness" alt="crowbusiness" class="image" /><br /> <img src="http://www.scp-wiki.net/local--files/scp-3466/mikeborb" alt="mikeborb" class="image" /><br /> <img src="http://www.scp-wiki.net/local--files/scp-3466/3466.JPG" alt="3466.JPG" class="image" /></div> </div> </div> <p>Okay, accidentally posted this early (don't ask how you accidentally post something, I feel really stupid), so I'm writing the author's post now instead of later. Yay! Yay&#8230; Anyways! This came out of Draft Swap, which is a little experiment put on by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/varaxous" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2433554&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1548004075" alt="Varaxous" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2433554)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/varaxous" >Varaxous</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2320004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1548004075" alt="Rimple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2320004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" >Rimple</a></span> in which people traded drafts that they had lost motivation for to other people. If it goes well, this could become a regular thing (and maybe get its own tag in the future, which would be awesome). I actually got stuck with Rimple's draft, which was just some lines of description and scribbled notes about a call in which someone is attacked by birds wanting money, and another log in which a D-Class enters a Burger King run by crows.</p> <p>Everything past those key points is conceptualized by yours truly, and Jimminy Christmas it has been fun.</p> <p>Rimple had a one off line about Wilson's Wildlife Solutions, and then I turned them into a whole GoI with a (what I felt to be) unique relationship with the Foundation, and furthermore a unique approach to anomalies (or unusualities). Special thanks to a whole <em>slew</em> of people who reviewed this, who I actually don't want to mention by name because I <em>will</em> forget some of them&#8230; but I'll do it anyways.</p> <ul> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2320004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1548004075" alt="Rimple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2320004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" >Rimple</a></span> (originator of the idea, key critiquer and helper outer)</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3938622&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1548004075" alt="The Great Hippo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3938622)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" >The Great Hippo</a></span> (gave the final polish on this article)</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=776854&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1548004075" alt="Tanhony" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=776854)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" >Tanhony</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/maliceaforethought" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2902864&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1548004075" alt="MaliceAforethought" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2902864)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/maliceaforethought" >MaliceAforethought</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1548004075" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009022&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1548004075" alt="not_a_seagull" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009022)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" >not_a_seagull</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1267048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1548004075" alt="Ihp" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1267048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" >Ihp</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tretter" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1422059&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1548004075" alt="tretter" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1422059)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tretter" >tretter</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zolgamax" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1707551&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1548004075" alt="Zolgamax" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1707551)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zolgamax" >Zolgamax</a></span></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3208919&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1548004075" alt="taylor_itkin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3208919)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" >taylor_itkin</a></span></li> <li>And more, I am sure!</li> </ul> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Alternate&nbsp;Titles</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Courtesy&nbsp;of&nbsp;Myself&nbsp;and&nbsp;Kirby</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>1:36 AM &lt;CaptainKirby&gt; The other title that I'd love for this is &quot;How to get away with business without really trying&quot;<br /> 1:37 AM &lt;CaptainKirby&gt; But that's because I know too many plays<br /> 1:37 AM &lt;DarkiOStuff&gt; “The Squawk of a Salesman”<br /> 1:37 AM &lt;CaptainKirby&gt; (&quot;How to get away with murder&quot; + &quot;How to succeed in business&quot;)<br /> 1:38 AM &lt;CaptainKirby&gt; &quot;HR's gonna get a hoot out of this&quot;<br /> 1:38 AM &lt;DarkiOStuff&gt; “Everything They Don’t Cheep You in Business School”<br /> 1:39 AM &lt;DarkiOStuff&gt; “Love, Life, and the Pursuit of Burger King”<br /> 1:39 AM &lt;CaptainKirby&gt; &quot;When I Crow Up I Wanna Be A Business Man&quot;</p> </div> </div> </div> <p>Oh, and uh, I usually <em>don't</em> do shameless self promotion in author posts&#8230; but they're author posts. So I am allowed to. <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1549">SCP-1549</a> &lt;&#8212; Another SCP I made recently that I think hasn't gotten much attention. It was posted in close proximity to a Kaktus skip on a week day, so that might have something to do with it, but still. It has some glowing reviews in the comments, and it would be nice if it just got more eyes. Also, if you think that I made cute crows, you might think I'm good at making beetles cute as well. You'll never know if you don't try it out, so if you want to see for yourself here is a handy link: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3018">SCP-3018</a> That's enough self promotion for one author's post. Check out my author's page if you like me in general. See y'all!</p> <p>Art at the top by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tickilung" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581130&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1548004075" alt="Tickilung" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581130)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tickilung" >Tickilung</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2320004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1548004075" alt="Rimple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2320004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" >Rimple</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hawks-n-coffee" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4544281&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1548004075" alt="Hawks n Coffee" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4544281)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hawks-n-coffee" >Hawks n Coffee</a></span>, and myself respectively, by the by.</p> 
				 	]]>
